query:
SELECT 
  id,
  dataVenda,
  YEAR(dataVenda) as ano_extraido,
  MONTH(dataVenda) as mes_extraido,
  valorTotal,
  excluido
FROM vendas
WHERE excluido = 0
ORDER BY dataVenda DESC
LIMIT 5
